  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hypothesis: Goal-directed echocardiography by trained critical care physicians is equivalent
      to that of echocardiography technicians/cardiologists for the purpose of determining etiology
      (reason) of cardiopulmonary failure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
